    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv I think the problem lies within \"InitializePromise\"-Component. Somehow when navigating from page A to page B, the subscription to `waitForResults` is renewed and resolves on the old page (`Page A`) - which at that point is unmounted.\r\n\r\n",
